flowchart TB
    GUI[图形界面] --> CFG[场景配置管理]
    CFG --> JSON[data/scene_profiles/*.json]

    IMGPIPE[图像分析管线] --> IMG[data/images]
    IMGPIPE --> DB[(SQLite数据库)]

    VIDPIPE[视频分析管线] --> MP4[data/videos]
    VIDPIPE --> PREJPG[data/video_previews/*.jpg]
    VIDPIPE --> META[data/video_previews/*.jsonl]

    DB --> T1[图片记录/检测结果/车道信息]
    DB --> T2[审核与扩展表结构]
